      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "This worked for me, thank you! The version tag did not resolve (I changed it to match my version of Maven) so I commented it out. I believe Maven should automatically fetch the correct latest version in that case, based on this thread: <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/17239394/maven-plugin-version-not-specified\" title=\"maven plugin version not specified\">stackoverflow.com/questions/17239394/&hellip;</a>."
