    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You need to go to Settings and set under the Java compiler the following:\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/OW3jL.png\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/OW3jL.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></a></p>\n\n<p>also check the Project Settings</p>\n"
