    "question_id" : 29888592,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>There are two ways to solve this problem:</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>Set settings <code>(File -&gt; Settings -&gt; Build, Execution, Deployment -&gt; Java Compiler)</code>:\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/4b9of.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/4b9of.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></a></li>\n<li>Add a build section to your <code>pom.xml</code>:\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/T7B1Z.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/T7B1Z.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></a></li>\n</ol>\n"
  }, {
