      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Thanks, Vishal. We have to specify project bytecode version, or at least per-module bytecode version with Intellij Idea. Just setting it in pom.xml for maven-compiler-plugin didn&#39;t solve the problem for me."
