    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>the below code working fine by my side. I just add it in the <strong><code>pom.xml</code></strong> file.</p>\n<pre><code>&lt;build&gt;\n    &lt;plugins&gt;\n        &lt;plugin&gt;\n            &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;\n            &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-compiler-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n            &lt;configuration&gt;\n                &lt;source&gt;1.8&lt;/source&gt;\n                &lt;target&gt;1.8&lt;/target&gt;\n            &lt;/configuration&gt;\n        &lt;/plugin&gt;\n    &lt;/plugins&gt;\n&lt;/build&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
